9. **만성 plasma-derived 1980s HIV/HCV contamination** = historical lesson — recombinant 폭발 + 2014+ EHL + 2017 emicizumab + 2022-24 gene therapy 4-wave paradigm shift. cytotoxic-only era 종료 + 만성 임상 의미 변화.
